snippet.title: Scifi Racing Team - Steam Next Fest: February 2025 Demo
snippet.description:
[WARNING: This game, possibly due to the budget and/or laziness, uses AI generated content for designers' helmet mesh, some UI SFX, background images used in the news screens and race track background visuals that are then blurred and used as a background for the game. Proceed with caution!]

A racing team manager that throws micromanagement out of the window. Lead your team to victory in various championships while adapting to new challenges over the seasons. Also, bots don't cheat.

Developed by Delicious Lines
Release Date: TBD

#steam #steamgames #steamgame #theforeseenarcade #steamnextfest #steamnextfestfebruary2025 #scifiracingteam
